{"tid":2411804,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我的初吻鍚咗落肥仔到","createTime":"2021-02-17T15:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T14:49:01.000Z","uid":228820,"like":26,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3dd65926a891a7b153ac39f1f76964e6a53d4442","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"我畢業了，但我死了。<br />\n<br />\n我從未嘗試拍拖，但我死了。<br />\n<br />\n我還是處子之身，但我死了。<br />\n<p class=\"left\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p><p class=\"right\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p>"},{"pid":"22114248d56baefc74a57987a5383d5ad99b1cf1","tid":2411804,"uid":376348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:05:45.000Z","msg":"祝幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8e97af93b2ffe9d8e0eb96096d9ef96df6cada","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"Ｈｉ錯制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b206cfd5d9915d8a1c1760e4d1f5cd2f08a48c09","tid":2411804,"uid":15739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"有無伸脷？"},{"pid":"17e1173698b5ccbd8177ca69f01a91f022a6babe","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:06:51.000Z","msg":"諗住試下排版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6ad15bbafdb0d8335d538b6e722f703822e26b","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:07:35.000Z","msg":"依度係故台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e76adcf4cd8d2931abee67eb8406a35261473a","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:07:51.000Z","msg":"我是被一架車撞死的。<br />\n<br />\n死後的世界我不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n我很想記起，卻記不起。<br />\n<br />\n我在白光中穿梭。<br />\n<br />\n直至我遇見一位擁有甜美笑容的女子。"},{"pid":"1d0a6e5cd9d96d4746c80d0e5707d903472c4c4f","tid":2411804,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"小學雞作文？"},{"pid":"09bc35bdfe182926564bb08c55f03c6abce8700e","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d0a6e5cd9d96d4746c80d0e5707d903472c4c4f","tid":2411804,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"小學雞作文？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:15:34.000Z","msg":"冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd8102d24be9eda9d39bd1f44e60328e1c15845","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"「你好！記唔記得你叫咩名？」佢同我講。<br />\n<br />\n「我好似叫紀依澄。」我用力想一想。<br />\n<br />\n「冇錯，你生前係叫紀依澄。」佢肯定了我的名字。<br />\n<br />\n「你係咪未想轉世呢? 你係咪有心願未了呢? 你好彩喇，有個人同我做咗個交易，只要你成功完成以下嘅挑戰，就可以回到人世。」佢開了一個條件給我。<br />\n<br />\n佢竟然睇得穿我的想法。<br />\n<br />\n「你係我面前係表露得一覽無遺㗎！」佢大笑地道。<br />\n<br />\n「咁係啊，但係我唔記得咗個心願係咩喎！」我已經想不起任何事情了。"},{"pid":"71145e5802a6188e630d9629ab4cdcfb2d07d1ad","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"「我好人，提埋你，你個心願係想同個男仔長廂廝守嘛！」佢偷笑。<br />\n<br />\n「你番落去你就會有番曬啲記憶㗎喇。」佢再補充。<br />\n<br />\n「事先講明遊戲規則，你要令到你嘅初吻能夠鍚在他的嘴唇上，而你只有五次機會，每次時限不一，會根據事件嘅長度嚟決定。你一定要喺五次內鍚到他的嘴唇，當然係要兩情相悅啦! 當你成功錫落佢個嘴唇到，你就可以重新做人喇。明白？」<br />\n<br />\n「明白！」我輕輕點一點頭。<br />\n<br />\n「咁祝你好運。」佢留下這一句就消失了。"},{"pid":"566e56d4f6302f874fe45d4ae11041087b92fab5","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:18:23.000Z","msg":"存貨冇曬喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31df924410c0c3292154bc7218ba89e577958cd9","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:21:48.000Z","msg":"１。 第一次機會<br />\n<br />\n「啊！啊啊啊呀哇！」我被一團炫目的白光吸入，離心力強大得使我忍受不住地哇哇大叫。<br />\n<br />\n「紀依澄！你上緊堂㗎，你尖咩叫啊！」一把刺耳的聲音從耳邊傳入。<br />\n<br />\n咦！ 我真係番咗嚟喎。<br />\n<br />\n我感動得落淚。<br />\n<br />\n「我問你點解上緊堂尖叫啫？唔洗喊掛。你快啲去廁所整理下你啲情緒啦。」<br />\n<br />\n聽著這種刺耳的聲音，我記起了她是誰。<br />\n<br />\n她是全校最出名的尖叫貓，嗓子永遠都高八度，令人覺得好刺耳。<br />\n<br />\n啊，我只有中一的時候上過她的課，即是我回到了中一的時候。<br />\n<br />\n「咁我去一去洗手間先啦！」我用一把哭聲回答，我覺得我要去廁所整理一下我身邊發生的事情。<br />\n<br />\n「拎埋去用！」一把幼稚的聲音把一包紙巾遞給我。<br />\n<br />\n「唔該！」我將目光望向聲音的主人，原來係你，男主角&mdash;文逸多。<br />\n<br />\n這時候的他一臉稚氣，身高還不如我。<br />\n<br />\n去到廁所，我打量一下當年的自己。<br />\n<br />\n一把過眼的齊蔭，剛長出的青春痘，尚未發育的胸部，一個小女孩的樣子。<br />\n<br />\n「估唔到我真係番到嚟，佢講過有五次機會，依家應該係第一次。」<br />\n<br />\n「但係中一嘅我可以做得啲咩呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「睇嚟第一次係比我適應一下。」我一路喃喃自語。<br />\n<br />\n我用冷水洗一洗臉頰，是冷的，即是這是一件真實的事情。"},{"pid":"bb6cfc4e05bdde28be5a4cae8f0df408573b893c","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"中意就留下正皮同留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔中意就留下你留言啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefbda8054846417372d13c39b7d7abbf98f0d70","tid":2411804,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63342ec2764497d5c346100b8f869aca4d712c41","tid":2411804,"uid":348457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:25:07.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"54ac29d802b41abac862e50368ab60284558add2","tid":2411804,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54cf4b107991731b55fc7ba92d34bea22f0d0cb","tid":2411804,"uid":387227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed15833465338415b7ea2833fb31dccb0f145796","tid":2411804,"uid":387227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:28:12.000Z","msg":"P牌冇得正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8867b2608ce4fe27a7cacd9b6cb2d120b05561","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aefbda8054846417372d13c39b7d7abbf98f0d70","tid":2411804,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:43:33.000Z","msg":"ＬＭ巴好耐冇見<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3cab6d3e3925505e9959294597dab54499efa2","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e54cf4b107991731b55fc7ba92d34bea22f0d0cb","tid":2411804,"uid":387227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打"},{"pid":"751181288adef2637159a928ae5ecffd1146a1db","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63342ec2764497d5c346100b8f869aca4d712c41","tid":2411804,"uid":348457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:25:07.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:18:01.000Z","msg":"謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35161d32c25720f40583797b30cda7bb8d27979","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:26:17.000Z","msg":"我慢慢地回到班房，好險，沒有人理會我。<br />\n<br />\n我一直都是一名被動的人，在班上亦是被標榜成一位文靜的同學。<br />\n<br />\n「冇事嘛？」他突如其來的關心把我嚇一跳。<br />\n<br />\n「冇。。冇事，你都專心上堂先。」我先話題中斷。<br />\n<br />\n「好吧！」他亦不強人所難，讓我獨自一下。<br />\n尖叫貓一聲令下就下課了。<br />\n<br />\n「你OＫ嘛？」他又一次關心我，這麼多年來，他一直都是一位貼心的人。<br />\n<br />\n「ＯＫ！我冇事了。」我交出一個微笑。<br />\n<br />\n「一起去食飯嗎? 有男有女的。」他一個善意的邀請。<br />\n<br />\n我裝作思考一下後就點頭。<br />\n<br />\n他們午膳的地方就正正是學校地下小食部。<br />\n<br />\n他們的午膳小組加上我總共有６人。<br />\n<br />\n在整個午膳時間裹我大多時都保持沉默。<br />\n<br />\n因為我正在想為什麼我會出現於這個時間點。<br />\n<br />\n應該是有一種可以改變的機會我才會出現。<br />\n<br />\n「依澄啊，你中意食咩啊?」在我思考的時候，一位眼大大樣子亦很可愛的女同學問。<br />\n<br />\n「我中意。。。」我望了文逸多一眼。<br />\n<br />\n「我中意嘅野食係朱古力。」我交出了一個很大眾化的答案。<br />\n<br />\n他們亦有附和說朱古力好食等等。"},{"pid":"b88c01880dd4ae621f6ae81ba6de01d87e743e37","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:33:28.000Z","msg":"得閒可以睇下小弟以下兩個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n短故   [我在召妓中重遇初戀]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2299029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2299029</a><br />\n<br />\n[唔好睇, 極短推理故] 我收到一份奇怪禮物<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2318384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2318384</a>"},{"pid":"f25a372daaa99842106d36e68c7ca85e75a261a5","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23e0619cc25657c95db5c99e962f389e7272cda","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f25a372daaa99842106d36e68c7ca85e75a261a5","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:23:08.000Z","msg":"薯皮冇得正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d3e3b239052fb0c52f2fae4bf867b8f53d2e09","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c23e0619cc25657c95db5c99e962f389e7272cda","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f25a372daaa99842106d36e68c7ca85e75a261a5","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:23:08.000Z","msg":"薯皮冇得正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:23:36.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab9b767c6b26afab2de462255113865ebf3ddda","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7d3e3b239052fb0c52f2fae4bf867b8f53d2e09","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c23e0619cc25657c95db5c99e962f389e7272cda","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f25a372daaa99842106d36e68c7ca85e75a261a5","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:23:08.000Z","msg":"薯皮冇得正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:23:36.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"睇嚟距離甩P仲有好耐日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0c87558bd809b371196dd572d8133c177c69aa","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ab9b767c6b26afab2de462255113865ebf3ddda","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7d3e3b239052fb0c52f2fae4bf867b8f53d2e09","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c23e0619cc25657c95db5c99e962f389e7272cda","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:23:08.000Z","msg":"薯皮冇得正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:23:36.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"睇嚟距離甩P仲有好耐日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:28:07.000Z","msg":"幫我推吓post<br />\n私語施凌同野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要努力post返晒上去"},{"pid":"26f38b8c08604f1158f2fcca717df582e70f8c2c","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:36:43.000Z","msg":"午膳時間被鐘聲打斷，我要獨自一人靜一下，便走先。<br />\n<br />\n我去了一個學校的秘密地點。<br />\n<br />\n這裡很少學生，沒有人會發現這裡。<br />\n<br />\n今天發生的事情十分之神奇，我由一個已死的靈魂一轉眼又回到中一時期。<br />\n<br />\n太不可思義了，但是那個任務真的很難去完成。<br />\n<br />\n想著想著，我就回到班房了。<br />\n<br />\n我一踏著課室裹，就看見我的筆袋劃出一個完表拋物線直中垃圾桶。<br />\n<br />\n「好耶！」原來拋我筆袋的人是一個高個子，打籃球的高手&mdash;鍾指峰。<br />\n<br />\n我為免添上麻煩，我默默地從垃圾桶中撿回我的筆袋。<br />\n<br />\n我把筆袋重新放回桌上，未竟，鍾指峰又一手奪去。<br />\n<br />\n他又再次做出投籃動作，我的筆袋又劃出一條完表拋物線，當它直準備投入垃圾桶的懷裡時，一雙巨大的手掌成功將它救起。<br />\n<br />\n「成功阻擋！哈哈！峰哥你要拋就拋依個，唔好拋人個筆袋啦！」他另一隻手拿起放在黑板上的粉刷，一下直接拋向鍾指峰身上。<br />\n<br />\n這個人就是文逸多了。<br />\n<br />\n「你！我唔會放過你的。」鍾指峰指著文逸多，然後氣急敗壞地走了。"},{"pid":"8f063f5013fc65fd96a67de0d460d4aa41416e11","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"文逸多一臉輕鬆地行過來，不，他本身就是坐在我左面，我們之間的距離只有一條走廊。<br />\n<br />\n「冇事喇，我成功保護咗你個筆袋！」他配上了一個充滿魅力的笑容。<br />\n<br />\n「多謝你，但係你唔驚得罪咗鍾指峰咩？」我仍有一點擔心他。<br />\n<br />\n「唔驚喎，佢都係玩玩下姐。」佢自信地答。<br />\n<br />\n後來我才知道他們是好兄弟，青梅竹馬那種。<br />\n<br />\n上堂的時候，文逸多他偷偷地送了我一盒薄荷朱古力豆，上面有一張便利貼。<br />\n<br />\n而便利貼上寫著「啱啱知你中意食朱古力，小食部只係得依一種，食咗就唔好唔開心喇。」<br />\n<br />\n紙上還畫了一個笑哈哈圖案。<br />\n<br />\n我向對面位的逸多，奉上一個真摰的笑容。<br />\n<br />\n我亦向他作出一個多謝你的口型。<br />\n<br />\n放學後，他好像要去操水，很快就走了。<br />\n<br />\n而我就自己一人返回家中，不知為何我的記憶完完整整出現在我的腦海之中。<br />\n<br />\n看著只有四面牆的家，我只好逃回我的小天地。<br />\n<br />\n我的小天地只不過是一張簡陋的睡床。<br />\n<br />\n我經歷了一天的突發事情，早已很想睡了。<br />\n<br />\n我一躺在床上就呼呼大睡了。"},{"pid":"4179b9ce934a480c5053235d4ba2286ebb86feec","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:48:46.000Z","msg":"在夢中的時間感覺很長，我好像不斷地在同一個位置地跑，永遠找不到出口。<br />\n<br />\n直至我被叮叮噹等的雜音吵醒。<br />\n<br />\n原來是我那個可愛細菌人鬧鐘叫醒我。<br />\n<br />\n咦！等等，這個鬧鐘明明是我中四那時買的，為什麼現在會出現呢?<br />\n<br />\n我摸一摸我的身體，噢，我胸前那兩顆肉團成功回來了。<br />\n<br />\n啊，我的頭顱突然很痛，有好多記憶湧現，這種感覺腦袋好像被人強行灌注了很多記憶。<br />\n<br />\n明明記憶中的人是我，但我又沒有經歷過。<br />\n<br />\n明明這是我第二次的記憶，但又很虛無縹緲。<br />\n<br />\n很辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n這種感覺令我很辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n隔了一會，頭終於沒有一開始那麼痛。<br />\n<br />\n我隨意地拿起一張紙和一支筆。<br />\n<br />\n我在紙上寫著幾點：<br />\n<br />\n１. 由一次穿越去下一次穿越之間發生的事會被強制加入和修正。<br />\n<br />\n２.  沒有<br />\n<br />\n對，我還未想到可以寫什麼。<br />\n<br />\n我把這張紙放在書桌的抽屜中，才看看日曆。<br />\n<br />\n大件事，今天是２０１８年３月２日，是我中學生涯的最後一日。<br />\n<br />\n原來我整整睡了６年。"},{"pid":"9fb026fab4e54eedc90f082f205350c0fcd7ac3b","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:10:42.000Z","msg":"我馬上去洗手間梳洗，十分鐘過後，我快手地收拾要準備的東西。<br />\n<br />\n在臨出門前，我看見一支母親大人專用的紅色唇膏躺在地上。<br />\n<br />\n我總覺得會有用，便把它放進我的袋子裡。<br />\n<br />\n我成功在學校關門前回去，還好沒有遲到。<br />\n<br />\nLast Day 的作用是讓一班同學們聚在一起，分享六年來的辛酸時候，拍下一些名為青春的照片。<br />\n<br />\n還有最重要的事情是在對方的校服上寫上各種加油或祝福字句。<br />\n<br />\n一整天都不是再上課，老師也不會阻礙我們享受青春的最後一天。<br />\n<br />\n「喂，逸多！」在我昏睡的六年間，我已經和文逸多和鍾指峰成為了好朋友。<br />\n<br />\n「咩事啊，依澄大小姐！」他是這樣叫我的。<br />\n<br />\n「幾時先會到我啊？」我拉一拉他的手臂。<br />\n<br />\n現在的他比起中一的時候高了很多，當然身材也脹了很多，但是在外在看起來也不覺得很胖，可能是他比較高的關係吧。<br />\n<br />\n「等我應付完我班粉絲先啦，你做壓軸嗰個啦！」他指著我道。<br />\n<br />\n「好啦，我先搵峰仔先啦，唔好唔記得我啊。」<br />\n<br />\n很快就找到峰仔，我馬上提筆一揮，在他校服上寫上「峰仔，估唔到同你成為好朋友，咁多年嚟多謝你，希望你早日出池啦，你永遠的好朋友紀依澄。」<br />\n<br />\n「你寫咗咩啊，峰仔?」我問正在我的背部寫字。<br />\n<br />\n「你番屋企咪知囉！咁心急做咩啊！放心我唔會喺你背上寫咩中意你好耐之類嘅說話嘅。」你一路寫一路笑。<br />\n<br />\n「哼，慌死你都唔會寫咩好嘢㗎啦！」我不服氣回答。<br />\n<br />\n峰仔向我吐一吐舌，做出一個滑稽的表情就跑走了。<br />\n<br />\n原來我的適應能力也很快，很快就能將那些回憶運用自如。<br />\n<br />\n經過一整天的忙碌，加上過了一個令人不捨的畢業典禮，放學的鈴聲也無情的響起。"},{"pid":"0269c156a597d83ac66d613192dc322c11756aff","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:35:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f91289a1bcd88e4be056534cc0ae2f4cde5770","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:35:25.000Z","msg":"得閒可以睇下小弟以下兩個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n短故 [我在召妓中重遇初戀]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2299029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2299029</a><br />\n<br />\n[唔好睇, 極短推理故] 我收到一份奇怪禮物<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2318384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2318384</a>"},{"pid":"91c56258cea1854057ec814d8d8766cf7514eb8a","tid":2411804,"uid":95032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:29:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f16cefd0e97b75b1d29365f64d20be318ff24f2c","tid":2411804,"uid":95032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:29:54.000Z","msg":"屌，打完推之後禁咗不推文回覆..."},{"pid":"1cae8ca9ae33ff497fceaa0a21e49d24a68508f4","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f16cefd0e97b75b1d29365f64d20be318ff24f2c","tid":2411804,"uid":95032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:29:54.000Z","msg":"屌，打完推之後禁咗不推文回覆..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:34:14.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f64afbf32c6aebc728ae0d9cd2e284e9ad5df97","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"此時我想起我還未在文逸多的校服上塗鴉。<br />\n<br />\n我在班房中找不到他，問了峰仔，他也不知道他在那裡。<br />\n<br />\n我細心回想，腦海中浮現出一個地方，就時當年我的秘密地點。<br />\n<br />\n我快步走過去，果然不出我所料，他在這裡。<br />\n<br />\n「點解你自己一個走咗過嚟，我差啲搵你唔到啊！係唔係想賣甩我！」我動氣地說。<br />\n<br />\n「依澄大小姐，唔好嬲，我知你一定搵到我嘅！」他用一個肯定的語氣說。<br />\n<br />\n「你又知我一定搵到你！」我不滿他要我搵他。<br />\n<br />\n「因為...」 他把臉轉過來。<br />\n<br />\n「因為什麼？」我有點手足無措。<br />\n<br />\n「因為你係最犀利囉！」他一臉正經地說無厘頭的說話。<br />\n<br />\n「係真唔係啊！」我望向他。<br />\n<br />\n「係啊，係咪同我影相啊?」<br />\n<br />\n佢打開電話的拍照功能，我倆頭貼頭拍了很多照片。<br />\n<br />\n當中包括很多鬼靈精怪的照片。<br />\n<br />\n「拎個背脊嚟，我要寫嘢。」我同佢講。"},{"pid":"5e54ccab3d170f1fc70255934fa9a6ea91dc25fa","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"過了一會後，他問：「你有幾多嘢要寫落嚟啊，好痕啊！」<br />\n<br />\n「等多陣啦，好快！」<br />\n<br />\n「你寫咗啲咩係我背脊啊？」<br />\n<br />\n「你番去咪知囉。」 此時我記得今早我順手拿了一支唇膏，我平均地塗在嘴上，然後一下吻在他背脊我的簽名傍。<br />\n<br />\n「我竟然收到依澄大小姐嘅吻！我真係幸運！」<br />\n<br />\n「只此一次，下不為例。」當我說完後，我立刻用吻來攻擊文逸多的左邊臉。<br />\n<br />\n他的左臉上有一個淡淡的唇印。<br />\n<br />\n他打算摸一摸塊臉，我立刻阻止並說：「唔好掂，我今日內見到唔見咗我地就絕交。」<br />\n<br />\n「好好好！」他只好放下手。<br />\n<br />\n「到我寫喇，你留咗邊個位比我寫啊？」他問。<br />\n<br />\n「我成個背脊都留咗比你喎！」<br />\n<br />\n「吓，只係背脊炸！」他露出一個失望的表情。<br />\n<br />\n「咸濕仔，寫你就寫啦！」我輕力打一打他。<br />\n<br />\n當逸多收筆的時候，峰仔一路跑一路大叫。<br />\n<br />\n「喂！你地原來喺度。個個都差唔多走曬喇。你地仲係到做咩啊？」<br />\n<br />\n「我地走喇！」逸多對我說。<br />\n<br />\n我點頭。<br />\n<br />\n「咦！多仔，點解你塊面有個唇膏印嘅？好似晏晝嗰陣都未有㗎。」 峰仔問。<br />\n<br />\n「多事啦你！」他拍一拍峰仔個頭，同一時間亦對我微笑。<br />\n<br />\n我想不到唇膏令到我踏進了一大步。"},{"pid":"49816a5bc6ed1b93749266f94ca236ade5a9badf","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:35:58.000Z","msg":"得閒可以睇下小弟以下兩個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n短故 [我在召妓中重遇初戀]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2299029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2299029</a><br />\n<br />\n[唔好睇, 極短推理故] 我收到一份奇怪禮物<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2318384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2318384</a>"},{"pid":"b268ef8e18dce70203175e32283fb195f407033d","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:22:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56458f46dca4636bc2528512d1d4910253a8146","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"好羨慕其他作者<br />\n好多人追文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42dce6b9af3de7f3b3bec98d180f3b0dd947336","tid":2411804,"uid":348457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:02:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"14a4a59879108b48cd918f33b2cd2a42d7176135","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c56458f46dca4636bc2528512d1d4910253a8146","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"好羨慕其他作者<br />\n好多人追文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T23:43:42.000Z","msg":"我都係"},{"pid":"7f57555ba41fe31e490a22193a7db34606f703ca","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f03806fef9b556dc663e1fb331ce8fafe2c3ff2","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:56:59.000Z","msg":"在我記憶中，全班一起影完大合照之後係去咗屯門一間派對房間去玩一晚。<br />\n<br />\n我們隨意影了張大合照就浩浩蕩蕩地出發。<br />\n<br />\n在坐輕鐵的時侯，我正在計劃一些能夠令文逸多主動吻在我嘴上。<br />\n<br />\n我知道他會因為家人致電而早走，到那時侯我跟他一起走就可以了。<br />\n<br />\n我相信我很快就可以完成任務。<br />\n<br />\n我一定做到的。<br />\n<br />\n人最開心是什麼？<br />\n<br />\n最開心就是有一班人可以陪你瘋瘋癲癲，把煩惱拋之腦後。<br />\n<br />\n這晚，大家都發表咗很多平日都不會說的話。<br />\n<br />\n有人哭著唱歌唱，有人仍然開開心心地打牌。<br />\n<br />\n我拿著了咪高峰，唱了一首首本名曲，最佳損友。<br />\n<br />\n我最怕有一天出現了這一句。<br />\n<br />\n為何舊知己 在最後 變不到老友。<br />\n<br />\n唱完後，掌聲響全場。<br />\n<br />\n而這時文逸多亦如歷史般的收到家人來電，要告辭了。<br />\n<br />\n「我都要走喇，我啊媽叫我走喇，各位再約啦。」 我同各位同學做出一個淑女離開動作。<br />\n<br />\n「咁我地一齊走啦，各位再見。」文逸多說。<br />\n<br />\n我點頭。<br />\n<br />\n在路上，我總覺得好像做留了一樣事情，但又記不起，就算了。<br />\n在等待西鐵的時候，逸多問了我一條問題。<br />\n<br />\n「究竟點樣先叫長大？」<br />\n<br />\n他冇事嘛，一來就問這樣深奧的問題。<br />\n<br />\n但是，我也不是省油燈。<br />\n<br />\n我想了一會，「當一個人唔想長大嘅時候就已經長大了。」<br />\n<br />\n他不斷喃喃自語，重複地說。<br />\n<br />\n不知他有什麼心事呢？<br />\n<br />\n我是否不應回答他呢。<br />\n<br />\n距離他回家也只有兩個站的距離，我也必須作出一些事情來完成任務。<br />\n<br />\n但是他好像好苦惱，我應不應該去打擾他呢？ <br />\n<br />\n最後我選擇了不打擾他，因為我相信我還有三次機會。<br />\n<br />\n我希望現在的他可以盡快擺脫煩惱。<br />\n<br />\n「咁我走先喇！遲啲見啦！」佢對仍在車廂的我說。<br />\n<br />\n「好啦！早抖！」我看著他左邊的臉說。<br />\n<br />\n幸好到現在我的唇印還在，我們不用絕交了。<br />\n<br />\n車門正慢慢關上，我望著逸多的背影，他的背影全部都是我的手作，一大堆密密麻麻的秀麗字，再加上一隻與他有幾分相似的細菌人。<br />\n<br />\n面對著忽然感到無力感的他，我選擇放棄這次機會。<br />\n<br />\n列車到站，稀疏的人流令我感覺得不真實。<br />\n<br />\n鞋帶鬆了，我蹲下身子，忽然間感到天旋地轉，看來時間到了。<br />\n<br />\n在失去意識前，我終於記得我忘記了什麼。<br />\n<br />\n原來我忘記了喝了多罐啤酒而睡著的峰仔。"},{"pid":"f84d0618132e7528a315cac1e7a0cb49b237e082","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0400e6a7f1a244579f6b6488a63d6f3f8f076748","tid":2411804,"uid":161406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T07:46:18.000Z","msg":"推，加油呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2cfd152c6e3f6a4aac508b785635db7cccc7f8","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0400e6a7f1a244579f6b6488a63d6f3f8f076748","tid":2411804,"uid":161406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T07:46:18.000Z","msg":"推，加油呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T07:48:59.000Z","msg":"巴打你幾時繼續寫啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb379a5e251a72ddb3dc7cb992e8b875626fa97","tid":2411804,"uid":161406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a2cfd152c6e3f6a4aac508b785635db7cccc7f8","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0400e6a7f1a244579f6b6488a63d6f3f8f076748","tid":2411804,"uid":161406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T07:46:18.000Z","msg":"推，加油呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T07:48:59.000Z","msg":"巴打你幾時繼續寫啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:08:09.000Z","msg":"下半年，依家最後一個sem，要趕Final year project <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你要加油！我會睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a52e8db0c2b6f5e3f98501c846d7db7d1cbf97","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fcb379a5e251a72ddb3dc7cb992e8b875626fa97","tid":2411804,"uid":161406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a2cfd152c6e3f6a4aac508b785635db7cccc7f8","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0400e6a7f1a244579f6b6488a63d6f3f8f076748","tid":2411804,"uid":161406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T07:46:18.000Z","msg":"推，加油呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T07:48:59.000Z","msg":"巴打你幾時繼續寫啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:08:09.000Z","msg":"下半年，依家最後一個sem，要趕Final year project <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你要加油！我會睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:09:13.000Z","msg":"我都係最後一個sem <br />\n好多嘢做緊<br />\n加油啊 等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1521b9cfbe7b2a5455d93e6ef772f32b829a2964","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a7285eab2f37e481ef1a4f48df196dd2c6539d","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91684abc608d2fc6beee9cf1dce1525df0d768d","tid":2411804,"uid":387227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好睇"},{"pid":"9cdfa0df1e6e625e7b8bf623fb2a1f616b517fc7","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T17:06:07.000Z","msg":"我又被細菌人鬧鐘吵醒了。<br />\n<br />\n這次我先看看月歷，確認日子比任何事都要緊。<br />\n<br />\n２０１８年７月１３日<br />\n<br />\n這次一睡就睡了足足半年，幸好只是半年而已。<br />\n<br />\n記憶照樣粗暴地灌進我的腦袋。<br />\n<br />\n可能只有半年記憶，這次沒有上次那麼痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n經過一段時間後，我明白為何我會出現在此。<br />\n<br />\n因為今天是去大學面試的一天。<br />\n<br />\n原本我是不想去的，無奈被他說之以情，動之以理地請過來。<br />\n<br />\n我們的分數並不高，只有全科剛好合格的分數。<br />\n<br />\n在殘留的記憶中，我記得因為我沒有帶齊文件而要來回走多了一轉。<br />\n<br />\n所以這次我細心檢查清楚所需文件，確保萬無一失才出門。<br />\n<br />\n去到約定時間，文逸多才施施出現。<br />\n<br />\n這個時候他的身型好像比半年前又脤了少少。<br />\n<br />\n一路上，我發現對比半年前他好像沉默了很多。<br />\n<br />\n可能還在思考那條問題？<br />\n<br />\n我也不知道。<br />\n<br />\n去到大學的附屬學院，我倆都因為以優秀的成績而獲得面試機會。<br />\n<br />\n而我們的面試官竟然是科目負責人。<br />\n<br />\n一走入去，光亮的環境使我感到很舒適。<br />\n<br />\n我和逸多並列而坐，面對嘴上掛著微笑的負責人。"},{"pid":"aad6a7169ace235dc7058df9a6d662131ade69a6","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b91684abc608d2fc6beee9cf1dce1525df0d768d","tid":2411804,"uid":387227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T17:06:28.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848c97f26d3dc594738ac3a7e402c65bae16c7e9","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458f520bfc97bcb73e59ea8f4714840ede736e25","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"848c97f26d3dc594738ac3a7e402c65bae16c7e9","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfed0c0ad41ba821b22e4bec226dd7e1dd7bc957","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:39:33.000Z","msg":"「你地應該都自我介紹過好多次啦？一定準備充足啦！」她輕笑兩聲。<br />\n<br />\n「今次你地嚟個特別啲嘅自我介紹，比一分鐘你地諗下，可以用動物／物件嚟介紹自己。」<br />\n<br />\n此時我心想，我沒有準備過自我介紹。<br />\n<br />\n「咁我講先啦！」逸多自告奮勇說。<br />\n<br />\n她點頭。<br />\n<br />\n「我會以獅子嚟形容自己。因為我...」我看著他充滿魅力的演講，我已經不能自拔了。<br />\n<br />\n「女仔你呢？」面試官問。<br />\n<br />\n我看他看得太入神了，忘記了我也是來面試的。<br />\n<br />\n我輕咳兩下，「我會選擇以刺蝟，本身我係一個好怕事嘅人，喺未識到朋友前，我都會好似刺蝟咁卷埋一舊，好彩我識到兩個好好嘅朋友，令我可以收番埋啲刺，同大家和洽相處。」我說得頭頭是道。<br />\n<br />\n面試完結後，文逸多一走出門外就問：「我係咪其中一個人呢！」他擺出一個神氣的姿勢。<br />\n<br />\n「係啊，多得你唔少啊！」我不理他，獨自走快兩步。<br />\n<br />\n我感覺到逸多在我後面偷笑。<br />\n<br />\n面試後的小朋友需要去詢問處遞交所需文件。<br />\n<br />\n由於我已經細心檢查清楚，所以很快就完成所有程序。<br />\n<br />\n我坐在面對詢問處的椅子，看著他七手八腳的模樣，我不小心笑了出來。<br />\n<br />\n幸好他聽不到。<br />\n<br />\n他掛著一副垂頭喪氣的樣子走過來。<br />\n<br />\n「做咩啊？交完文件個人唔同曬樣嘅?」我問。<br />\n<br />\n「唉，唔知點解我拎漏咗份嘢，佢叫我今日內比番佢，我要白白走一轉啊，你話係咪好麻煩！」他向我抱怨。<br />\n<br />\n「你快啲番去拎番啦，我喺依度等你！」我把他趕走。<br />\n<br />\n「但係你要喺依度等好耐喎！」他有點猶豫。<br />\n<br />\n「去啦，文逸多！」要我做出投擲精靈球的動作，他才急急腳地走。<br />\n<br />\n「等我！」他留下一句話。"},{"pid":"aa70f7427a5aa45580c3aba6d02fd6219dbc4666","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbcef69903af79e3d6ea189a967b242bfc6dd49","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"在等待他的這兩個半小時內，我有什麼事可以做呢?<br />\n<br />\n我發現了一件事，在原本的記憶中，是我忘記帶齊文件，要他等我兩個小時。<br />\n<br />\n但我明明做出了改變，可是結局我還是要等這兩個小時。<br />\n<br />\n是不是同樣的結局，但是不同的劇本呢?<br />\n<br />\n即是我無論點努力也好，也不能改寫一早注定的結局?<br />\n<br />\n還是這只是一次巧合？<br />\n<br />\n剛好忘記？<br />\n<br />\n想著想著，逸多他已經成功交回文件。<br />\n<br />\n他交回後就走到我面前，雙眼看著我雙眼，四目交接。<br />\n<br />\n「終於番嚟喇！」我問。<br />\n<br />\n「係啊，辛苦你等我咁耐，嗱，依個當係賠禮！」汗水沿著他的髮髻到下巴。<br />\n<br />\n我連忙拿出紙巾給他，看來他為了縮短時間，應該很努力地跑來跑去。<br />\n<br />\n「唔該！」他接下紙巾後，我才察覺他手上的禮物。<br />\n<br />\n「咩嚟㗎？」我看著一個很像蛋糕盒的盒子問。<br />\n<br />\n「係你中意嘅朱古力蛋糕。知你等咗我好耐，應該都肚餓喇，咪買個細蛋糕嚟食下囉」他一路抹汗一路說。<br />\n<br />\n「好啦！放過你啦，都算你有良心，原諒你啦。」我答。<br />\n<br />\n「多謝依澄大小姐嘅皇恩浩蕩！」他沒正經地說。"},{"pid":"aa68185efaae89f99ff2a7ec99a1cc0ee9877f81","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"想快啲完咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7739e391a456f9a2d6f830779ac2c34c78c1c161","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa68185efaae89f99ff2a7ec99a1cc0ee9877f81","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"想快啲完咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n我反而想新故寫長少少<br />\n之前兩個故都係3-4萬字"},{"pid":"a118228d69029b5a63fd3eb7e0e238556355a113","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7739e391a456f9a2d6f830779ac2c34c78c1c161","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa68185efaae89f99ff2a7ec99a1cc0ee9877f81","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"想快啲完咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n我反而想新故寫長少少<br />\n之前兩個故都係3-4萬字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:49:29.000Z","msg":"依個故應該大約一萬字<br />\n我想開新故<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1634667510603f2b43cd264370ae1e9b594e7837","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"他叉了一粒朱古力給我。<br />\n<br />\n我亳不猶豫地連朱古力帶叉地一口食落去。<br />\n<br />\n「喂！我隻叉啊！」他想從我口中強行抽出。<br />\n<br />\n「唔緊要啦！」我口齒不清地說。<br />\n<br />\n我再用叉叉了一大舊蛋糕，然後遞出給他。<br />\n<br />\n他一下遲疑，還是一口食下去。<br />\n<br />\n「你食咗我口水尾啊，要聽我話喎！」我挑釁他。<br />\n<br />\n「聽你個頭啊，你用咗我隻叉，係咪要聽我話啊！」他反問。<br />\n「係啊！」我沒有猶疑地答。<br />\n<br />\n「吓！咁順攤嘅！」他好像被我的率直嚇到。<br />\n<br />\n我望著他，希望他能感受到我的心意。<br />\n<br />\n他望著我，好像在想想台詞。<br />\n<br />\n「嗯？」<br />\n<br />\n「咩...咩啊，望住我做咩啊！」他慌張地答。<br />\n<br />\n「冇嘢喇！」我發脾氣了。<br />\n<br />\n「喔！」<br />\n<br />\n就這樣，在回家的路上，他不斷找我說話，我也冷淡地回答。<br />\n<br />\n他好像察覺到我的不快，他的面上呈現出糾結的表情。<br />\n<br />\n最後他決定閉嘴。<br />\n<br />\n直至他下車，我倆只有說過再見。<br />\n<br />\n唉，唔通他不喜歡我嗎？<br />\n<br />\n好明顯這次又失敗了。<br />\n<br />\n我只剩下兩次機會了。"},{"pid":"18e52233ffbefcaacc05999348985f423b07bc35","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:42:20.000Z","msg":"我今日出咗好多文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398518680fbbbafe3b0f02f3d21734d94769c5b1","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:19:54.000Z","msg":"４。第四次機會<br />\n<br />\n我被陽光照耀。<br />\n<br />\n我醒了。<br />\n<br />\n這次應該係第四次機會。<br />\n<br />\n我必須把握這兩次機會。<br />\n<br />\n記憶修正帶來的痛楚，我已經慢慢習慣了。<br />\n<br />\n頭很痛，但我習慣了。<br />\n<br />\n我望向月歷，今天又是什麼日子。<br />\n<br />\n今天是２０１８年８月１６日，明天是我的生日。<br />\n<br />\n記憶完成修正，原來今天文逸多和鐘指峰兩人約我去街。<br />\n<br />\n死人文逸多，竟然要借峰仔嚟約我。<br />\n<br />\n哼，無膽匪類。<br />\n<br />\n我換好衣服後，便提著袋子出去了。<br />\n<br />\n去到約定時間，一身肌肉的峰仔和有一個大肚腩的文逸多已經到了。<br />\n<br />\n「早晨！」「早啊！」他們異口同聲地說。<br />\n<br />\n「早啊兩位！今日你地諗住去邊?」我問。<br />\n<br />\n「去食早餐先囉！」峰仔說。<br />\n<br />\n「好啊！」我答。<br />\n<br />\n「出發！」<br />\n<br />\n我們去到一間平常去開的茶餐廳快速吃了一個方便的早餐。<br />\n<br />\n吃過早餐後，他們二人帶我去睇戲。"},{"pid":"5afc17b1be58890b65fc18e9e4b1c1af75167b4a","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:20:17.000Z","msg":"就嚟完故喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3975b8fb5aad95ee13b4df20521f03c66e70c84b","tid":2411804,"uid":389111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5afc17b1be58890b65fc18e9e4b1c1af75167b4a","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:20:17.000Z","msg":"就嚟完故喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c445d5ce7355b15914d113bb6b81f9e42e5098be","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"戲院的環境漆黑一片，伸手不見五指。<br />\n<br />\n峰仔坐左我的右邊，逸多坐在我的左邊。<br />\n<br />\n我正吃著他們買的甜鹹爆谷，看著一套關於吸血鬼的卡通片。<br />\n<br />\n我用雙脾夾住桶爆谷，打算拿我放在左手邊的汽水，誰能料這時我竟捉到了一隻大手。<br />\n<br />\n我想一想誰坐在我的左手邊，原來是肥仔文逸多。<br />\n<br />\n不知為何我沒有放手，他也沒有鬆開我的手。<br />\n<br />\n未竟，他一個反手直接拖著我的手。<br />\n<br />\n我手上濕漉漉，不知是誰的手汗。<br />\n<br />\n就這樣，他整套戲一直拖著我，直至離場。<br />\n<br />\n在完場時，我倆終於把手鬆開。"},{"pid":"58278d7d825ca629bb0196f6809a457e50f3101c","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經消失咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f0f1f7295b9e6011981423ce55929eeb1b13b6","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"大家想睇happy end 定 sad end ?<br />\nhappy end 正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsad end 負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5931c77376e0294ff5c0b94f29e7eee915a75f71","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"「好唔好睇？你地好似有啲奇怪喎。」峰仔問。<br />\n<br />\n「邊有啊！」我控制著我的心跳和面部表情。<br />\n<br />\n「咪係！」逸多附和道。<br />\n<br />\n「咁你地今日玩得開心啲，我有啲急事要做。」峰仔識趣地說。<br />\n<br />\n「吓！咁掃興。」逸多說。<br />\n<br />\n「再見！」「拜拜！」<br />\n<br />\n峰仔走後，空氣變得很尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n我望著逸多，他亦望著我。<br />\n<br />\n都不知道我們對望了多久。<br />\n<br />\n「不如去行下，附近幾靚㗎！」他率先打破沉默。<br />\n<br />\n「好啊！」我想我是紅著臉來答。<br />\n<br />\n我跟著他在商場中左穿右插，看到精品店和衣店就進去看看。<br />\n<br />\n快樂的時間特別快，天色也慢慢變黑。<br />\n<br />\n「我想去一去廁所，等我一陣！」<br />\n<br />\n「好啊！」<br />\n<br />\n為什麼女廁永遠都要排隊？<br />\n<br />\n為什麼不可以站著去廁所？<br />\n<br />\n出到廁所後，我看見文逸多有點站立不安。<br />\n<br />\n「出嚟喇?」<br />\n<br />\n「係啊，等好耐?」我問。<br />\n<br />\n我們的氣氛有點尷尬，又有點曖昧。"},{"pid":"8ff9af00330308cfc62bbb6a86ab00f7557fa1a0","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T18:46:36.000Z","msg":"「係啊，我買咗份禮物比你啊！」他有點害羞地說。<br />\n<br />\n「咩嚟㗎！」我從他手上拿個一份盒子。<br />\n<br />\n我小心翼翼地打開盒子，發現是一條銀色的手鏈。<br />\n<br />\n「哇！好靚啊。」我真心覺得很適合我。<br />\n<br />\n「不如我幫你帶啦！」<br />\n<br />\n「好啊！」我相信我應該不能容易地戴上。<br />\n<br />\n他細心地捉著我隻手，把手鏈穿上。<br />\n<br />\n我的心砰通砰通地跳。<br />\n<br />\n「搞掂！」<br />\n<br />\n「好襯你啊！」他由衷地說。<br />\n<br />\n「係咩！多謝你！」我細細聲說。<br />\n<br />\n「咁我地去食飯好唔好?」他溫柔地說。<br />\n<br />\n「你中意啦！」<br />\n<br />\n「咁我地去食鋸扒啦!好唔好!」<br />\n<br />\n「好啊!」<br />\n<br />\n去到一個裝修精湛，別具特色的一間餐廳。<br />\n<br />\n「你幫我揀啦，我咩都食！」在進去前我跟文逸多說。<br />\n<br />\n「好啊，我會揀好嘢比你食嘅！」他說得頭頭是道。<br />\n<br />\n「今日有咩推介?」 文逸多問。<br />\n<br />\n「今日T-骨唔錯啊!」侍應推薦。<br />\n<br />\n「咁兩份７成熟啦！一份黑椒汁，一份洋蔥汁。」<br />\n<br />\n「好！多謝」<br />\n<br />\n「你又知我唔食辣嘅！」我問。<br />\n<br />\n他做了一個自滿的表情。<br />\n<br />\n「哼！懶巴閉！」<br />\n<br />\n侍應把熱得滋滋作響的鐵板放在我們面前。<br />\n<br />\n「我唔客氣喇！」我對著文逸多說。<br />\n<br />\n我把熱騰騰的牛柳切開並放進口中，口感軟腍，幼嫩多汁，好惹味。<br />\n<br />\n「好食啊！」<br />\n<br />\n「好食就好喇！」<br />\n<br />\n我在文逸多面前，表演了一個絕技。<br />\n<br />\n我在他面前以龍捲風來襲的方式，一下子把枱面的美食清光。<br />\n<br />\n看到我光速把食物清光的文逸多面上露出一個驚訝的表情。<br />\n<br />\n當然我也有像一個淑女般用紙巾把我的櫻桃小嘴抹乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n逸多都很快把所有食物清光。<br />\n<br />\n甜品是焦糖布甸。<br />\n<br />\n我輕試一口，好甜，好好味。<br />\n<br />\n「係咪好好食?」<br />\n<br />\n「係啊！」<br />\n<br />\n「你食埋佢啦！」他把他的布甸放到我面前。<br />\n<br />\n「咁我唔客氣喇！」我直接吃他的布甸。<br />\n<br />\n他一直看著我，使我感到十分不自在。<br />\n<br />\n「做咩係咁望住我？」我害羞地問。<br />\n<br />\n「因為你最犀利囉！」<br />\n<br />\n「哼！無厘頭！」但我的嘴角是向上的。<br />\n<br />\n我再一次把布甸吃得一乾二淨。<br />\n<br />\n「走lu!」我說。<br />\n<br />\n「好啦！」<br />\n<br />\n又去到熟悉的地鐵站了。"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e5d7f5b04952c714ced96e8008473b286a86fdc9","tid":2411804,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"大家得閒可以睇下以下幾個高質故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好睇又好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［愛情/武俠］《暮晨》我只係想溝女 點解要我打打殺殺<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aHtMsoU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aHtMsoU</a><br />\n<br />\n《樓主講古直播中》<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gBzJjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gBzJjS</a><br />\n<br />\n【第二季】《三天之後，遊戲開始。》【冒險】【少少愛情】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gFBCCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gFBCCS</a>"}}